In re John Wesley CASH. No. 346P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Oct. 14, 2015. Peggy Ann Duff, Brevard, for Duff, Peggy Ann. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Transylvania County.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 13th of October 2015 by Petitioner for Emergency Injunctive Relief:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of October 2015."
